@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000/api
@token = replace-with-supabase-access-token

### Mensagem de hoje
GET {{baseUrl}}/messages/today
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Criar mensagem manual como draft
POST {{baseUrl}}/messages
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Amor que serve",
  "title_en": "Love that serves",
  "content": "Jesus chama-nos a amar com gestos concretos e humildes.",
  "content_en": "Jesus calls us to love through concrete and humble acts.",
  "bible_reference": "Joao 13:34",
  "theme": "amor"
}

### Aprovar mensagem
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/messages/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000/approve
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Agendar mensagem aprovada
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/messages/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000/schedule
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "publish_date": "2026-05-03T08:00:00.000Z"
}

### Gerar mensagem com IA como draft
GET {{baseUrl}}/ai/agents
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Gerar mensagem com IA como draft
POST {{baseUrl}}/ai/generate-message
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "theme": "perdao",
  "bible_reference": "Mateus 18:21-22"
}

### Criar artista
POST {{baseUrl}}/artists
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Criador Exemplo",
  "instagram_handle": "@criador",
  "bio": "Criador autorizado para colaboracoes."
}

### Aprovar artista
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/artists/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000/approve
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "permission_status": "approved"
}

### Criar reel original
POST {{baseUrl}}/reels
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Recomecar com Jesus",
  "title_en": "Beginning again with Jesus",
  "caption": "Hoje ha graca para recomecar.",
  "caption_en": "Today there is grace to begin again.",
  "video_url": "https://cdn.example.com/reels/recomecar.mp4",
  "source_type": "original"
}

### Aprovar reel
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/reels/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000/approve
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Agendar reel aprovado
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/reels/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000/schedule
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "scheduled_at": "2026-05-03T18:30:00.000Z"
}

### Publicar imagem aprovada imediatamente
POST {{baseUrl}}/instagram/publish-image
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "caption": "O amor de Cristo permanece.",
  "media_url": "https://cdn.example.com/images/amor.jpg"
}
